verbose_text: As determined by western blot analysis, PAECs treated with the let-7d agomir and ATG16L1 overexpression vectors displayed significantly elevated levels of ATG16L1 and significantly elevated ratios of LC3-II to LC3-I but significantly reduced expression of p62 compared with PAECs treated with the let-7d agomir and oe-NC vectors (P < 0.05; XREF_FIG).
